                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "You attach the wheels to your feet, and their constant movement and energy allow you to move through the air. You gain a fly Speed of 20 feet for 10 minutes. While in use in this way, you can\u2019t wield the wheels as weapons. You can spend an Interact action at any time to end this effect and re-grip the heavenly rolling flames. If you lack enough free hands to wield them, you drop them in your space.",
